    "name": "禁忌艺术",
    "steam_appid": 1166140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Forbidden Art 是一款 VR 逃生解谜游戏，在游戏中，您要从杀手的秘密巢穴中逃出。<br>从地牢开始，穿过秘密通道、书房、停尸房、通风口、小教堂等，在不被凶手发现的情况下逃出生天。<br><br><br><br><strong>::主要功能::</strong><br><br>🔹 <strong>逼真的图形</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/3a16e7e7f0d41546b465ac0789ce30c8.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/3a16e7e7f0d41546b465ac0789ce30c8.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/3a16e7e7f0d41546b465ac0789ce30c8.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>VR 的魅力在于它能让玩家完全沉浸在环境中。我们在制作背景时注重真实感，让玩家获得极致的沉浸式体验。在 VR 中感受杀手的巢穴--韩国一个偏远村庄中由废弃小教堂改建而成的巢穴。<br><br><br>🔹 <strong>旋转和高度调节</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/ba49f77cedd7c98bdea9fa6ae9c35157.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/ba49f77cedd7c98bdea9fa6ae9c35157.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/ba49f77cedd7c98bdea9fa6ae9c35157.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/c1dac0bb717aab7e838c0bcec65705c0.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/c1dac0bb717aab7e838c0bcec65705c0.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/c1dac0bb717aab7e838c0bcec65705c0.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>该功能是专为坐着玩游戏或因健康原因无法长时间站立的玩家添加的。<br>旋转功能可提供即时、流畅的旋转，让玩家选择自己想要的游戏方式。<br>高度调节提供了蹲姿、站姿和混合模式，玩家只需一个按钮就能同时操作两种模式。<br>坐好，放松，享受《Forbidden Art》的乐趣！<br><br><br>🔹 <strong>光源</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/69b3febb83280ee20fdfcf6256e50e9f.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/69b3febb83280ee20fdfcf6256e50e9f.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/69b3febb83280ee20fdfcf6256e50e9f.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏中有些地方非常暗，没有光源就无法前进。在这些区域，您可以使用打火机或手电筒来帮助您看得更清楚。<br><br><br>🔹 <strong>可写的日记</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/e36bedec0149bef2d5962fdd88f00876.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/e36bedec0149bef2d5962fdd88f00876.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/e36bedec0149bef2d5962fdd88f00876.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>虽然不记笔记也能解开所有谜题，但为了加快某些部分的解题速度，同时也为了玩家的整体乐趣和方便，我们增加了记笔记的功能。<br><br><br>🔹 <strong>6m X 6m 房间比例模式</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/18d0e5f6cc426806193d2877198d5698.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/18d0e5f6cc426806193d2877198d5698.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/18d0e5f6cc426806193d2877198d5698.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《Forbidden Art》是一款支持“6m X 6m Roomscale 模式”的 VR 游戏。<br>游戏的整个地图是为了适应 6m X 6m 的现实世界空间而构建的，玩家实际上可以在游戏中的所有空间中走动和玩耍，而不仅仅是按下控制器上的按钮。<br>如果玩家可以使用 6m X 6m 的游戏区域，我们强烈建议使用“6m X 6m 房间规模模式”进行游戏。<br><br>当然，我们意识到并非所有玩家都能使用 6m x 6m 的空间。<br>因此，我们还提供了“控制器移动模式”，让没有空间的玩家可以不受任何限制地在VR中享受“禁忌艺术”。<br><br><br>🔹 <strong>数百个可交互的物体</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/2f5e5ff1975b79587d2ec40da614c31f.poster.avif?t=1729575706\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/2f5e5ff1975b79587d2ec40da614c31f.webm?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1166140/extras/2f5e5ff1975b79587d2ec40da614c31f.mp4?t=1729575706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>您可以抓取游戏中的几乎所有物体并进行交互，其中一些物体具有特殊的交互作用。<br><br><br><br>🔸 有些谜题可能非常具有挑战性。然而，所有的线索都在你被困的空间里。使用你库存中的物品，仔细观察空间，寻找逃脱的方法。<br>运用你所有的能力逃离一个由精神病杀手创造的危险而可怕的藏身处！<br><br><br><strong>::注意::</strong><br>第一次开始游戏之前，请确保您周围有足够的空闲空间，<br>周围没有家具或任何其他物品，佩戴耳机时可能会造成伤害。<br>确保所有运动控制器已充满电。",
